cs.CR, cs.IT, cs.CC, cs.CY, cs.SE 

This paper discusses the improvement of the McEliece cryptosystem based on LDPC codes, which is a topic related to cryptography (cs.CR) and information theory (cs.IT). The use of irregular LDPC codes is also discussed, which is a topic related to coding theory (cs.CC). The investigation of the efficiency of the system is also mentioned, which can be related to computer systems and networking (cs.CY) and software engineering (cs.SE).
